placed team of the [[Montenegrin Second League|Second League]]) and the 11th-placed team (against the runners-up of the Second League) will both compete in two-legged relegation play-offs after the end of the season.\n\n===First legs===\n{{football box\n|date= 3 June 2012\n|time= 17:30 CEST\n|team1= [[FK De\u010di\u0107|De\u010di\u0107]]\n|score= 0\u20130\n|report=\n|team2= [[FK Jedinstvo Bijelo Polje|Jedinstvo]]\n|goals1= \n|goals2= \n|stadium= \n|attendance=\n|referee  =}}\n----\n{{football box\n|date= 3 June 2012\n|time= 17:30 CEST\n|team1= [[FK Berane|Berane]]\n|score= 1\u20132\n|report=\n|team2= [[FK Mornar|Mornar]]\n|goals1= [[Nikola Tomovi\u0107|Tomovi\u0107]] {{goal|7}}\n|goals2= {{goal|10}} [[Sa\u0161a Jovovi\u0107|Jovovi\u0107]]<br />{{goal|68}} [[\u0110or\u0111e Vojvodi\u0107|Vojvodi\u0107]]\n|stadium= \n|attendance=\n|referee  =}}\n\n===Second legs===\n{{football box\n|date= 7 June 2012\n|time= 17:30 CEST\n|team1= [[FK Jedinstvo Bijelo Polje|Jedinstvo]]\n|score= 2\u20130\n|report=\n|team2= [[FK De\u010di\u0107|De\u010di\u0107]]\n|goals1= [[Nemanja Goja\u010danin|Goja\u010danin]] {{goal|21}}<br />[[Nemanja Goja\u010danin|Goja\u010danin]] {{goal|42}}\n|goals2= \n|stadium= \n|attendance=\n|referee  =}}\n----\n{{football box\n|date= 7 June 2012\n|time= 17:30 CEST\n|team1= [[FK Mornar|Mornar]]\n|score= 3\u20130\n|report=\n|team2= [[FK Berane|Berane]]\n|goals1= [[Mustafa Metovi\u0107|Metovi\u0107]] {{goal|8}}<br />[[Mustafa Metovi\u0107|Metovi\u0107]] {{goal|26}}<br />Jovan\u010dov {{goal|33}}\n|goals2= \n|stadium= \n|attendance=\n|referee  =}}\n\n==Top scorers==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"  \n|-\n!Rank\n!Scorer\n!Club\n!Goals\n|-\n|rowspan=\"1\" align=\"center\"|1\n|{{flagicon|MNE}} [[Admir Adrovi\u0107]]\n|[[FK Budu\u0107nost Podgorica|Budu\u0107nost]]\n|align=\"center\"|22\n|-\n|rowspan=\"1\" align=\"center\"|2\n|{{flagicon|MNE}} [[\u017darko Kora\u0107]]\n|[[FK Zeta|Zeta]]\n|align=\"center\"|21\n|-\n|rowspan=\"1\" align=\"center\"|3\n|{{flagicon|SRB}} [[Ivica 