 had a baby girl on November 23, 2014.<ref name=\"Daughter\"/> He also has a son named Eugene Jr.<ref name=\"Son\"/> Hilton, whose given name is Eugene, explained how he became known as T. Y.: \"My daddy\u2019s name is Tyrone, so ever since I was little, everyone has just used the first two letters of that.\"<ref name=\"Time to recover\">{{cite web|last1=Beas|first1=Mike|title=Time to recover: Speedy rookie receiver off to fast start|url=http://www.therepublic.com/view/local_story/Time-to-recover-Speedy-rookie-_1348546232|website=Franklin (IN) Daily Journal|accessdate=November 25, 2014|date=September 25, 2012|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141218104052/http://www.therepublic.com/view/local_story/Time-to-recover-Speedy-rookie-_1348546232|archivedate=December 18, 2014}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|30em}}\n\n==External links==\n{{commonscat}}\n* {{Football stats |nfl=2532865 |espn=14924 |pfr=H/HiltT.00}}\n* [http://www.colts.com/team/roster/T.Y.-Hilton/1bfc81a4-87be-4e0e-bc21-25099996be55 Indianapolis Colts bio]\n* [https://fiusports.com/roster.aspx?rp_id=2171 FIU Panthers bio]\n\n{{Indianapolis Colts roster navbox}}\n\n{{NFL receiving yardage leaders}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Hilton, T.Y.}}\n[[Category:1989 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:American Conference Pro Bowl players]]\n[[Category:American football wide receivers]]\n[[Category:FIU Panthers football players]]\n[[Category:Indianapolis Colts players]]\n[[Category:Players of American football from Florida]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople from Miami]]\n[[Category:Unconferenced Pro Bowl players]]\n", "name_user": "Red Director", "label": "safe", "comment": "date formats perMOS:DATEFORMATbyscript- Reference edited withProveIt", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/T._Y._Hilton"}
